    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it's not just feelings. i look at them and i just see how much more they could achieve if they weren't constantly fighting my mistakes or worrying about me. it feels like the only way i can actually protect them or give them a real chance is if i wasn't in the picture. it's almost like the most loving thing i could do is just... stop being a problem for them.",
