      "content": "i hear what u say about therapists but it feels so theoretical. it doesn't change the fact that my existence is literally draining them of their happiness. it feels so selfish to keep dragging them down with me just so i can feel \"needed.\" if i just went away, they could finally focus on themselves and actually thrive without my shadow hanging over everything. doesn't it make sense that the kindest thing for them would be for me to just be gone?",
